sequenceDiagram
    participant App as Application
    participant EM as EntityManager/Session
    participant Hibernate as Hibernate Core
    participant Listener as Event Listener

    App->>EM: Perform entity operation (e.g., save, update, delete)
    EM->>Hibernate: Delegate operation
    Hibernate->>Listener: Trigger pre-event (e.g., PreInsertEvent)
    Listener-->>Hibernate: Listener processes event (can modify entity)
    Hibernate->>Hibernate: Perform main operation (e.g., insert into DB)
    Hibernate->>Listener: Trigger post-event (e.g., PostInsertEvent)
    Listener-->>Hibernate: Listener processes event (e.g., logging, auditing)
    Hibernate-->>EM: Return control
    EM-->>App: Operation complete
